### FIX 2 — VIX/VIX3M ratio for Layer 2 (15 min)
**File:** `backend/app/signals/kill_chain.py`, Layer 3 GEX block  
```python
import yfinance as yf
vix_data = yf.download(["^VIX", "^VIX3M"], period="1d", progress=False)
vix = float(vix_data["Close"]["^VIX"].iloc[-1])
vix3m = float(vix_data["Close"]["^VIX3M"].iloc[-1])
ratio = round(vix / vix3m, 3) if vix3m else 0
# ratio > 1.0 = backwardation = dealer stress = layer_2 triggered
```

### FIX 3 — Position persistence (20 min)
**Files:** `backend/app/signals/kill_chain.py` + state read/write logic  
Add `position` object to `kill_chain_state.json`.  
Implement entry/pnl/deactivation logic on state transitions.

